window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Brought to you by Penguin.</b></p> <p><i>‘There is some kind of magic in you somewhere.’</i><br> <br> This edition of <i>Matilda</i>, part of The Roald Dahl Classic Collection, is perfect for Dahl fans old and new.<br> <br> So, enter a world where invention and mischief can be found on every page and where magic might be at the very tips of your fingers . . .<br> <br> The Roald Dahl Classic Collection reinstates the versions of Dahl’s books that were published before the 2022 Puffin editions, aimed at newly independent young listeners.</p>"; 
